Van Hool NV  will build most of new
orders for 510 buses outside of  Belgium , De Tijd  reported  today.  Van Hool has two orders to build buses for the U.S. market
and will manufacture 300 low-cost vehicles in a new
manufacturing facility outside Belgium to save on labor costs,
the newspaper said. The company hasnâ€™t yet decided on the
